		<img itemprop="image" sizes="" class="progressive-image-large" alt="A competitor participates in the Tough Mudder challenge near Winchester in southern England October 25, 2014.  REUTERS/Luke MacGregor  (BRITAIN - Tags: SPORT SOCIETY ATHLETICS) - RTR4BK4H" title="" srcset="https://qzprod.files.wordpress.com/2017/02/tough-mudder-jumping-through-air.jpg?quality=80&amp;strip=all&amp;w=320 320w, https://qzprod.files.wordpress.com/2017/02/tough-mudder-jumping-through-air.jpg?quality=80&amp;strip=all&amp;w=640 640w, https://qzprod.files.wordpress.com/2017/02/tough-mudder-jumping-through-air.jpg?quality=80&amp;strip=all&amp;w=940 940w, https://qzprod.files.wordpress.com/2017/02/tough-mudder-jumping-through-air.jpg?quality=80&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1600 1600w, https://qzprod.files.wordpress.com/2017/02/tough-mudder-jumping-through-air.jpg?quality=80&amp;strip=all&amp;w=3200 3200w" src="https://qzprod.files.wordpress.com/2017/02/tough-mudder-jumping-through-air.jpg?quality=80&amp;strip=all&amp;w=320">
		<noscript>
			&lt;img src="https://qzprod.files.wordpress.com/2017/02/tough-mudder-jumping-through-air.jpg?quality=80&amp;strip=all&amp;w=320" alt="A competitor participates in the Tough Mudder challenge near Winchester in southern England October 25, 2014.  REUTERS/Luke MacGregor  (BRITAIN - Tags: SPORT SOCIETY ATHLETICS) - RTR4BK4H" title=""&gt;
		</noscript>
	</picture>
	<figcaption class="featured-image-caption">
		<div class="content-width-responsive">
			<i class="icon-camera"></i>It's not about being superhuman—it's about becoming more human.							<span class="featured-image-credit has-space"> (Reuters/Luke MacGregor)</span>
					</div>
	</figcaption>
</figure>
<div class="item-content ">
	<div class="item-meta">
